1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,320
Hello everyone and welcome to EnglishPod.
大家好，欢迎收听EnglishPod。

2
00:00:03,320 --> 00:00:04,320
My name is Marco.
我是Marco。

3
00:00:04,320 --> 00:00:05,320
Hi everyone.
大家好。

4
00:00:05,320 --> 00:00:09,280
My name is Kathryn and today we have an elementary level lesson for you.
我是Kathryn，今天我们为大家准备了一节初级课程。

5
00:00:09,280 --> 00:00:10,280
That's right.
没错。

6
00:00:10,280 --> 00:00:15,360
Today we are dealing with a house that is filled with different types of bugs.
今天我们要讲一个房子里到处都是各种虫子的事。

7
00:00:15,360 --> 00:00:16,360
Ew, bugs.
呃，虫子。

8
00:00:16,360 --> 00:00:21,960
Well, it's summertime so it's not that uncommon but not a pleasant thing to deal with.
嗯，现在是夏天，所以这并不罕见，但处理起来可不是什么愉快的事。

9
00:00:21,960 --> 00:00:22,960
That's right.
没错。

10
00:00:22,960 --> 00:00:24,560
So we're going to call an exterminator.
所以我们打算叫一个灭虫员。

11
00:00:24,560 --> 00:00:29,480
So you might be asking yourself what that is but before we explain, why don't you listen
你可能在想那是什么，但在我们解释之前，不如先听一遍

12
00:00:29,480 --> 00:00:32,400
to the dialogue for the first time.
对话。

13
00:00:32,400 --> 00:00:46,600
Hi, did you call for an exterminator?
你好，是你叫的灭虫员吗？

14
00:00:46,600 --> 00:00:49,240
Yes, thank goodness you're here.
是的，谢天谢地你来了。

15
00:00:49,240 --> 00:00:51,280
These bugs are driving us crazy.
这些虫子快把我们逼疯了。

16
00:00:51,280 --> 00:00:53,880
What sort of pests are we dealing with?
我们遇到的是什么害虫？

17
00:00:53,880 --> 00:00:57,680
We just bought this house and it is infected with just about everything.
我们刚买了这栋房子，它几乎被所有东西侵占了。

18
00:00:57,680 --> 00:01:02,200
We have termites in the wood, cockroaches all over the place and last night I saw a
木头里有白蚁，到处都是蟑螂，昨晚我还看到一只

19
00:01:02,200 --> 00:01:05,320
huge rat out in the backyard.
巨大的老鼠在后院。

20
00:01:05,320 --> 00:01:07,200
Well there's nothing that we can handle.
嗯，没有我们处理不了的。

21
00:01:07,200 --> 00:01:11,120
I'll spray the floorboards and walls to get rid of the cockroaches but the termites will
我会喷洒地板和墙壁来消灭蟑螂，但白蚁会更难处理。

22
00:01:11,120 --> 00:01:12,640
be harder to get rid of.
更难清除。

23
00:01:12,640 --> 00:01:15,560
We will have to cover the entire house and fumigate it.
我们必须覆盖整栋房子并进行熏蒸。

24
00:01:15,560 --> 00:01:19,580
Unfortunately, that means you will have to find a place to stay for the next three days.
不幸的是，这意味着你接下来三天得找个地方住。

25
00:01:19,580 --> 00:01:20,640
No problem.
没问题。

26
00:01:20,640 --> 00:01:29,720
Let's get rid of the bugs.
咱们把这些虫子消灭掉吧。

27
00:01:29,720 --> 00:01:30,720
Alright we're back.
好了，我们回来了。

28
00:01:30,720 --> 00:01:32,920
So now we have six key words that we've chosen out for you.
现在我们为你挑选了六个关键词。

29
00:01:32,920 --> 00:01:39,920
